Package: vMF
Title: Sampling from von Mises-Fisher Distribution
Version: 0.1
Date: 2019-03-22
Authors@R: person("Elysee Aristide", "Houndetoungan", email = "ariel92and@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Elysee Aristide Houndetoungan [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Elysee Aristide Houndetoungan <ariel92and@gmail.com>
Description: Provides fast sampling from von Mises-Fisher distribution use the method proposed by Andrew T.A Wood (1994) <doi:10.1080/03610919408813161>. Unlike 'movMF' of Kurt Hornik and Bettina Gr√ºn (2014) <doi:10.18637/jss.v058.i10> the mixtures on von Mises-Fisher distributions are not consider. However, fast sampling frow the distribution are particulary regarded here. Advanved examples available \href{<https://houndetoungan.wixsite.com/aristide/fast-sampling-from-vmf-distribution>}{online} show how fast the sampling is and its usefulness.
